{"article_id":"q7yQeJNacYUebV82","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The future of Brett Kavanaugh 's nomination to the Supreme Court is now in the hands of the Senate after Thursday 's dramatic and historic hearing .","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"Now it 's up to a few senators from both parties to decide","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"if he 'll be confirmed ,","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"and the voting process begins Friday morning .","depth":2},{"id":4,"text":"The intense hearing gripped the nation for an entire day .","depth":3},{"id":5,"text":"Dr. Christine Blasey Ford and Judge Brett Kavanaugh both gave emotional testimonies about what they remember from 1982 .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"It began with an emotional accusation of sexual assault from Dr. Christine Blasey Ford ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"followed by a vehement denial from Judge Kavanaugh .","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"`` I am here today","depth":15},{"id":9,"text":"not because I want to be .","depth":15},{"id":10,"text":"I am terrified , ''","depth":14},{"id":11,"text":"she told the Senate panel .","depth":13},{"id":12,"text":"`` I am here","depth":13},{"id":13,"text":"because I believe","depth":14},{"id":14,"text":"it is my civic duty to tell you what happened to me","depth":15},{"id":15,"text":"while Brett Kavanaugh and I were in high school . ''","depth":15},{"id":16,"text":"When asked how certain she was","depth":13},{"id":17,"text":"that Kavanaugh was the one","depth":14},{"id":18,"text":"who assaulted her ,","depth":14},{"id":19,"text":"Ford replied ,","depth":13},{"id":20,"text":"`` 100 percent . ''","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"READ :","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Republicans to Vote 'Yes ' on Kavanaugh","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"After Sen. Jeff Flake Agrees to Advance His Nomination","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"Dr. Ford described that traumatic moment in as much detail","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"as she could recall .","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"`` Brett groped me","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"and tried to take off my clothes , ''","depth":14},{"id":28,"text":"she said .","depth":14},{"id":29,"text":"`` I believed","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"he was going to rape me . ''","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"She said","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"she has no doubts","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"it was Brett Kavanaugh and Mark Judge","depth":14},{"id":34,"text":"who were in the room","depth":15},{"id":35,"text":"and attacked her .","depth":15},{"id":36,"text":"Sen. Patrick Leahy","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"( D-VT )","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"asked her ,","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"`` What is the strongest memory","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"you have ? ''","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"Dr. Ford replied ,","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"`` The uproarious laughter between the two .","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"And their having fun at my expense . ''","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"Then Judge Kavanaugh took his turn","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"where he categorically denied her claims .","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"`` I 'm here today","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"to tell the truth .","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"I 've never sexual assaulted anyone , not in high school , not in college , not ever , ''","depth":14},{"id":49,"text":"Kavanaugh said .","depth":14},{"id":50,"text":"He said","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"while he believes","depth":15},{"id":52,"text":"something may have happened to Dr. Ford ,","depth":15},{"id":53,"text":"he did not do it .","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"He provided his actual calendar from 1982 ,","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"which included details","depth":15},{"id":56,"text":"about where he was and what he was doing every day ,","depth":15},{"id":57,"text":"arguing","depth":14},{"id":58,"text":"that it was evidence","depth":15},{"id":59,"text":"that he could n't have been at the party","depth":16},{"id":60,"text":"where the attack occurred .","depth":16},{"id":61,"text":"He became emotional ,","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"repeatedly fighting back tears","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"as he talked about the impact of the accusations on him and his family .","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"Kavanaugh said ,","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"`` The other night , Ashley and my daughter , Liza , said their prayers .","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"And little Liza","depth":17},{"id":67,"text":"- all of 10 years old -","depth":17},{"id":68,"text":"said to Ashley ,","depth":16},{"id":69,"text":"'We should pray for the woman . '","depth":15},{"id":70,"text":"That 's a lot of wisdom from a 10-year-old . ''","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"Kavanaugh told","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"how this process has damaged his family and destroyed his good name ...","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"consequences","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"that will follow them for decades .","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"He pointed out his lifelong goals","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"of helping women advance in the judiciary and teaching the next generation of children ,","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"but his reputation is so damaged","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"he may never be able to teach law or to coach sports again .","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"`` I love coaching more than anything","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"I 've ever done in my whole life .","depth":14},{"id":81,"text":"But thanks to what some of you on this side of the committee have unleashed ,","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"I may never be able to coach again , ''","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"he said through tears .","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"Kavanaugh confronted Democrats head-on ,","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"calling the process an orchestrated and calculated political hit job .","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"`` This confirmation process has become a national disgrace .","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"The Constitution gives the Senate an important role in the confirmation process ,","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"but you have replaced advice and consent with search and destroy , ''","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"Judge Kavanaugh assured senators","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"no matter what , he 's not backing out of this process .","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"`` You may defeat me in the final vote ,","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"but you 'll never get me to quit .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"Never , ''","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"As soon as they got the chance ,","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"some Republicans unleashed their anger on Democrats","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"for dragging Judge Kavanaugh and his family through the mud in an effort ,","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"they say ,","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"to score political points ahead of the midterms .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"Sen. Lindsey Graham","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"( R-SC )","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"passionately pointed a finger of blame at the Democrats on the committee","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"saying ,","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"`` If you wanted an FBI investigation","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"you could have come to us .","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"What you wanted to do was destroy this guy 's life , and hold this seat open","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"and hope","depth":14},{"id":109,"text":"you win in 2020 ,","depth":14},{"id":110,"text":"you 've said that ...","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"This is the most unethical sham","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"since I 've been in politics . ''","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"Sen. Orrin Hatch","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"( R-UT )","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"said ,","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"`` This is a national disgrace , the way","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"you 're being treated . ''","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"Pastor Robert Jeffress ,","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"who sits on the president 's evangelical advisory board ,","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"says","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"Democrats demonstrated how far they 'll go","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"to protect abortion rights .","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"`` The hearings put the hypocrisy of the Democrats on full display , ''","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"he says .","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"`` When we all know","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"that their number one objection to Judge Kavanaugh is that he might restrict in some way the murder of 700,000 females every year in the womb through abortion . ''","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"But","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"even if Kavanaugh is confirmed ,","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"Democrats believe","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"Dr. Ford served as a credible witness","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"who will energize their voter base come November .","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"Sen. Dick Durbin","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"( D-IL )","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"said ,","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"`` She was credible , calm .","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"She told us","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"she was terrified ,","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"but I thought","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"she handled the questions professionally and honestly . ''","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"Appearing on 's Faith Nation","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"Republican National Committee Spokeswoman Kayleigh McEnany praised the way","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"Kavanaugh handled Ford 's accusation .","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"`` He does not disbelieve Ms. Ford ,","depth":14},{"id":144,"text":"he believes","depth":16},{"id":145,"text":"something very terrible could have happened to her ,","depth":16},{"id":146,"text":"but it just was n't him that did it .","depth":15},{"id":147,"text":"So he was very compassionate toward her ,","depth":14},{"id":148,"text":"but very strong and very unmistakable in denying these allegations .","depth":14},{"id":149,"text":"He swore before God , ''","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"she said .","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"A relieved President Trump tweeted ,","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"`` Judge Kavanaugh showed America","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"exactly why I nominated him . ''","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"The Senate Judiciary Committee is expected to advance Kavanaugh 's nomination to the full Senate ,","depth":3},{"id":155,"text":"and procedural action over the weekend will set up a potential confirmation vote as early as Tuesday .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":311,"left":159,"right":310,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":158,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":158,"left":0,"right":157,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":157,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":310,"left":308,"right":309,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":308,"left":4,"right":307,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":307,"left":249,"right":306,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":249,"left":5,"right":248,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":248,"left":236,"right":247,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":236,"left":176,"right":235,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":176,"left":173,"right":175,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":6,"right":172,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":172,"left":7,"right":171,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":166,"right":170,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":166,"left":162,"right":165,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":162,"left":161,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":160,"right":10,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":160,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":12,"right":164,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":164,"left":13,"right":163,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":163,"left":14,"right":15,"relati